*Nade* su da će se situacija promeniti (There is hope that the situation will change).
*Ona je svoje nade polagala u njega* (She put her hopes in him).
*Nade* su da će se stvari promeniti u bolje (There is hope that things will change for the better).
*On je izgubio sve svoje *nade* (He lost all of his hope).
*Gde god da se okrene, ona vidi *nade* (Wherever she turns, she sees hope).